author: Cleo Abram
description:
The world’s most famous robot dog can now do backflips! You all remember Spot, the viral robot dog from Boston Dynamics. Well, now he can do backflips! 

But why does that matter? And how did it learn?Turns out it’s surprisingly important…

title: This Robot Dog Can Do A New Trick
